'''Mercy Falls''' is a book written by [[William Kent Krueger]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.buffalolib.org/vufind/Record/1631343|title=Holdings: Mercy Falls /|website=www.buffalolib.org|language=en|access-date=2017-03-23}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.williamkentkrueger.com/books/mercy-falls/|title=Mercy Falls: Excerpt - William Kent Krueger|work=William Kent Krueger|access-date=2017-03-23|language=en-US}}</ref> and published by [[Pocket Books]] (owned by [[Simon & Schuster]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.simonandschuster.com/books/Mercy-Falls/William-Kent-Krueger/Cork-OConnor-Mystery-Series/9781439157800|title=Mercy Falls {{!}} Book by William Kent Krueger {{!}} Official Publisher Page|last=|first=|date=|website=Simon & Schuster|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=}}</ref>) on 16 August 2005, which later went on to win the [[Anthony Award]] for Best Novel in 2006.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.bouchercon.com/anthony-awards/winners-and-nominees/2000s/|title=Winners and Nominees 2000s|date=2015-09-22|work=Bouchercon|access-date=2017-03-23|language=en}}</ref>
